ide.backend.collections

Class WireFrame

  • java.lang.Object
    • ide.backend.collections.WireFrame

  • public class WireFrame
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains the entire wireframe from the current program Every instance placed in this wireframe and all his wires (to other instances, labeled with an event), are stored in the WiredInstances

    Axel
